1. To compile simply open a terminal and run Make

2. To run, do ./render then <drivername> and <outputfile>
eg: ./render driver5.txt output.ppm


A note is that the program defaults to 8 threads, to change this change the NUM _THREADS defined on top of the program

custom driver is known as driver5.txt, will run as displayed above, resolution is at 512 x 512. 

the included output is also at 512 x 512
